From: roku <Thunderoar>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 20:30:12 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 8/8] fix: Exynos AWB override, black level config, prefs
 caching, and preview lag fix
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Patches in Shamim.smali:
- Remove AWB debug logging spam
- GetAwbGain(): return unity gains [1.0,1.0,1.0,1.0] on Exynos
- GetBlackLevel(): read 4 user-configurable black levels on Exynos
- GetDefaultString(): cache SharedPreferences in static field
- GetSliderPref(): preview lag fix v2 — override CONTROL_MODE,
  STATISTICS_FACE_DETECT_MODE, AE_TARGET_FPS_RANGE, and
  STATISTICS_OIS_DATA_MODE to fix Exynos HAL reprocessing pipeline
---
 smali_classes3/sgcam/Shamim.smali | 235 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 227 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

